# Simple Todo List

A clean and responsive Todo List application built with vanilla JavaScript, HTML, and CSS.

## Features

- Add new todo items
- Remove items with fade animation
- Responsive design
- Clean, modern UI
- Input validation

## Getting Started

1. Clone this repository
2. Open `index.html` in your browser

## Project Structure

- `index.html`: The main HTML file that includes the Todo List application.
- `app.js`: The JavaScript file that handles the application logic.
- `app.css`: The CSS file that styles the Todo List application.
